<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NTM10.10">
<l>nallaveṉ ṟōḻi nāka ṇaimicai namparar</l>
<l>celvar periyar ciṟumā ṉiṭavarnām ceyvateṉ</l>
<l>villi putuvai viṭṭucit tartaṅkaḷ tēvarai</l>
<l>valla paricu varuvippa rēlatu kāṇṭumē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>My good friend! Our God on the serpent bed is wealthy [and] superior.</l>
<l>What can we, little humans, do?</l>
<l>If Viṣṇucitta of Villi Putuvai makes their Lord come in ways that [he] can,</l>
<l>we shall see Him [then].</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
